{"type":"message","id":"b835aca3","parentId":"ffeedd3c","timestamp":"2026-03-09T07:38:24.086Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"需要尝试使用 API 获取中国石油的历史 K 线数据，直接查询 3 月 6 日收盘价。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我看到网页上有**历史数据**,但浏览器的快照中没有显示具体的历史 K 线数据。让我访问专业的行情数据接口:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5aa6fd588bcc4f65ab3f6eff","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock && python3 << 'EOF'\nimport requests\nimport json\n\nurl = \"https://push2his.eastmoney.com/api/qt/stock/kline/get\"\nparams = {\n    \"secid\": \"1.601857\",  # 上海市场 + 601857\n    \"fields1\": \"f1,f2,f3,f4,f5,f6\",\n    \"fields2\": \"f51,f52,f53,f54,f55,f56,f57,f58,f59,f60,f61\",\n    \"klt\": 102,  # 日线 K 线\n    \"fqt\": 1,\n    \"beg\": \"20260301\",\n    \"end\": \"20260309\"\n}\n\nheaders = {\n    \"User-Agent\": \"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36\",\n    \"Referer\": \"https://quote.eastmoney.com/sh601857.html\"\n}\n\ntry:\n    resp = requests.get(url, params=params, headers=headers, timeout=15)\n    data = resp.json()\n    \n    if data.get(\"data\"):\n        klines = data[\"data\"].get(\"klines\", [])\n        \n        print(\"=\" * 100)\n        print(f\"{'日期':<10} {'收盘':<8} {'开盘':<8} {'最高':<8} {'最低':<8} {'成交量 (手)':<15} {'成交额 (万)':<15}\")\n        print(\"-\" * 100)\n        \n        for line in klines[-10:]:  # 最近 10 个交易日\n            parts = line.split(\",\")\n            if len(parts) >= 7:\n                date = parts[0]\n                close = f\"{float(parts[1]):.2f}\"\n                open_p = f\"{float(parts[2]):.2f}\"\n                high = f\"{float(parts[3]):.2f}\"\n                low = f\"{float(parts[4]):.2f}\"\n                vol = f\"{int(float(parts[5])/100):,}\"\n                amt = f\"{float(parts[6])/10000:.2f}\"\n                \n                print(f\"{date:<10} {close:<8} {open_p:<8} {high:<8} {low:<8} {vol:<15} {amt:<15